title: Warlords II Deluxe for DOS
material_description: CD-ROM videogame. CD-ROM in CD jewel case
brief_description: An updated version of the original game, Warlords II Deluxe adds higher resolution graphics, new terrain types, new scenarios and improved AI. It also allows for the creation of custom tile, army, and city sets for the map. The game is bundled with an improved version of the Warlords II Scenario Builder.
